# Thread Carousels - API Keys
# Not all keys are required. See README.md for which skills need which keys.

# Image generation (Gemini) - for AI-generated carousel images
# Get yours at: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key

# Image search (Tavily) - for finding reference images
# Get yours at: https://tavily.com
TAVILY_API_KEY=your_tavily_api_key

# GIF search (Giphy) - for animated GIF slides
# Get yours at: https://developers.giphy.com
GIPHY_API_KEY=your_giphy_api_key

# Cloud browser recording (Steel) - for screen demo skill
# Get yours at: https://steel.dev
STEEL_API_KEY=your_steel_api_key
